"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"There is a conflict between Fedorov and Commander-in-Chief Oleksandr Syrskyi, which influenced Zelensky's decision. Polish security services claim the goal was to create ethnic tensions between Poland and Ukraine.\",            \"english_title\": \"Conflict and Tensions\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay un problema entre Fedorov y el Comandante Oleksandr Syrskyi, que influy\u00f3 en la decisi\u00f3n de Zelensky. Los servicios de seguridad de Polonia dicen que el objetivo era crear tensiones entre Polonia y Ucrania.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Problema y Tensiones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The air quality in parts of Michigan, Minneapolis, and Minnesota is considered very bad by authorities.\",            \"english_title\": \"Bad Air Quality\",            \"translated_version\": \"La calidad del aire en partes de Michigan, Minneapolis y Minnesota es considerada muy mala por las autoridades.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mala Calidad de Aire\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Argentina might face punishment from Fifa because their players celebrated the World Cup semi-final win against England with a banner supporting their country's claim to the Falkland Islands.\",            \"english_title\": \"Argentina Faces Fifa Punishment\",            \"translated_version\": \"Argentina podr\u00eda ser castigada por Fifa porque sus jugadores celebraron la victoria en la semifinal del Mundial contra Inglaterra con un cartel apoyando el reclamo de su pa\u00eds sobre las Islas Malvinas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Argentina y Castigo de Fifa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Explosions were heard in Iran overnight, soon after nearby Gulf states reported attacks.\",            \"english_title\": \"Explosions in Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"Se escucharon explosiones en Ir\u00e1n durante la noche, poco despu\u00e9s de que estados cercanos del Golfo reportaran ataques.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosiones en Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The former head of Italy's motorway operator, Giovanni Castellucci, received a 12-year sentence for the 2018 bridge collapse.\",            \"english_title\": \"Italy Bridge Collapse Sentence\",            \"translated_version\": \"El exjefe de la operadora de autopistas de Italia, Giovanni Castellucci, recibi\u00f3 una sentencia de 12 a\u00f1os por el colapso del puente en 2018.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Sentencia por Colapso de Puente en Italia\"        }    ]}"